<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.9.7">
<l>viḷaṅkaṉiyai yiḷaṅkaṉṟu koṇṭutira veṟintu vēlneṭuṅka ṇāycciyarkaḷ vaittatayir veṇṇey</l>
<l>uḷaṅkuḷira vamutuceytiv vulakuṇṭa kāḷai ukantiṉitu nāṭōṟum maruviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>iḷampaṭinaṟ kamukukulait teṅkukoṭic cennelīṉkarumpu kaṇvaḷarak kāltaṭavum puṉalāl</l>
<l>vaḷaṅkoṇṭa peruñcelvam vaḷarumaṇi nāṅkūr vaikunta viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Vaikunta Viṇṇakaram in lovely Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where great bounty grows, which gains fertility by the waters</l>
<l>Which overflow the channels so that the tender type of good areca nuts,</l>
<l rend="indent">clustered coconuts, creepers, red paddy,</l>
<l rend="indent">and sweet sugarcane nodes grow,</l>
<l>The temple where dwells the young man,</l>
<l rend="indent">happily with affection [and] rejoicing daily, who, having taking up a young calf,</l>
<l rend="indent">throwing [it] so woodapples fell,</l>
<l>Consumed this world, having eaten to his heart’s content,</l>
<l rend="indent">the curds and ghee stored by the herdesses with long lance[-like] eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
